data.description: Ready to move to Florida and enjoy an active retired lifestyle? The Royal Harbor is a well appointed active adult community filled with activities for you to enjoy!  This beautiful home is ready for you! Enjoy new paint inside and out, a spacious kitchen and a natural gas grill on your screened lanai!  This well maintained home is a three bedroom, two bathroom split plan that is highly functional in design.  The owner had a UV light installed on the new HVAC system that sanitizes air flow in the home. Additional benefits include the 30amp RV hookup and generator plugin, already installed. In the garage you'll find a treasure trove of storage and countertop for the hobbyist. Enjoy peaceful living in this well built home!  This is must see in Royal Harbor, an amenity filled gated community!
